description:
This round will determine the winner of April's Tag Team Match! Both teams are giving it their all, and the fight for victory is brutal. It will all come down to one question, who wants it more?
In the end we call the match just a little early due to an accidental headbutt. But regardless of this little snafu, the winners of this match have already been determined. Stay tuned for Round 4 where you can see the winning team strap-on fuck the losers!
title: Rd 3/4 April's Tag Team: Final Round to determine the winner! Live non-scripted sexual wrestling!!
